description: This file defines the ConnectorsPage component for managing connectors in a React frontend application. It includes UI for listing, creating, and deleting connectors, and handles interactions with API functions.

methods.name: load
methods.description: Asynchronously loads the list of connectors from the API.

methods.name: remove
methods.description: Deletes a connector by ID after user confirmation.

methods.name: submit
methods.description: Handles the creation of a new connector by calling the API.
